<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Jusbid Group Hotel Welcome Email</title>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: 'Poppins' !important;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div
		style="max-width: 800px; margin: 15px auto; border: 1px solid #fff; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;border:1px solid #666">
		<div style="padding: 20px 15px; text-align: center;">
			<img src="https://jusbid.in:1337/images/logo_jusbid.png" alt=""
				style="width:200px;height:100%;object-fit: contain;">
		</div>
		<div style="text-align: center">
			<h2 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;font-size: 2.2em;color:#000000">Welcome, your group hotel account has been accepted.
			</h2>
			<h4 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;color:#000000">{{createdAt}}</h4>
			<button style="background-color: #25D366;
			color: #ffffff;
			border-radius: 10px;
			border: none;
			padding: 10px 40px;">Welcome to Jusbid Family</button>
		</div>
		<div style="margin:30px 0px;">
			<img style="width:100%" src="{{full_image_path}}">
		</div>
		<div style="padding: 30px 15px; color: #333; font-size: 14px;">
			<div>
				<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
					<strong>{{name}}</strong>,
				</p>
			</div>

			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
                A very warm welcome from JusBid
                We hope this message finds you well.  We are reaching out to you in reference to your esteemed hotel properties listings on our OTA platform, JusBid.in. It is our great pleasure to inform you that your registration process as a Business partner is successfully completed.
                We are likewise looking forward to long term business associations and business development together. We are here to take an interest in the New Business Process for the Industry. Your support and participation is really appreciated to fulfil our mission of bridging the gap between customers and hoteliers. Our executive will reach out to you shortly regarding any assistance required for the next steps regarding hotel properties management over Justbid.in. In case of any queries, please feel free to reach out to our support team at support@jusbid.in. <br><br>
				<br><br>
				Please follow steps given below to check your hotelier panel:
				<br>
				1. Click below button or visit <span
					style="font-style: italic;text-decoration: underline;">https://www.jusbid.in/portal/#/partner/hotelier</span><br>
                2. Select Multi Chain Login Option in the Login Form.

                3. Enter registered E-mail which you have used to register all hotels and select the check box for group hotel.
                
                4. Select the hotel from the drop down below which you want to log into. 
                
                5. Enter the password generated by the system which is mentioned below (if you are facing an issue to find password, please contact support).
                
                6. Now you can easily manage your hotel appearance, rooms, bidding, bookings and much more.

			</p>
			<table style="width: 100%">
				<tr>
					<td width="30%">OnBoarded Hotels</td>

					<td width="70%">

                        <% hotels.forEach(function(hoteldata, index) %>
                            <strong>{{hoteldata.name}}</strong>
                         <% } %>
                    
                    </td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width="30%">Registered Email</td>
					<td width="70%"><strong>{{email}}</strong></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>Your Password</td>
					<td><strong>{{password}}</strong></td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<p style="padding: 10px;text-align:center;">
				<a href="https://www.jusbid.in/portal/#/partner/hotelier" target="_blank" style="background-color: #25D366;
					color: #ffffff;
					border-radius: 10px;
					border: none;
					padding: 10px 40px;">
					<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.8px;">Visit Hotelier Panel</span>
				</a>
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;">Thank you,</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;"><strong>Team Jusbid.</strong></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>